Use these locations:

- /components : reusable UI components (e.g., Header, Footer, SEO).
- /pages : route pages and API routes under /pages/api.
- /hooks : React hooks (e.g., useAuth, useLogout, useTokenSync).
- /lib : helpers and utilities (if added later).
- /public : static assets.
  Do not place feature logic inside /pages components when it belongs in /hooks or /lib.
